    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "exc_list",
      "x": 776,
      "y": 566,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 190,
      "text": "knowledge vault + FTS index   filesystem + SQLite\n(~8GB corpus, lexical search - not a doc DB fit)\norg-partitioned: the firm's documents never pool across orgs\nsandboxes, per-app git, browser profiles   filesystem\nevent queue (webhook dedup + retry)   SQLite (P-06)\nblobs: screenshots, files, PDFs   filesystem (P-07)\n\nP-08 retired: the Supabase control plane is folded into\nFirestore - credentials, orgs and activation now live\nin the same database (see collections at left).",
      "originalText": "knowledge vault + FTS index   filesystem + SQLite\n(~8GB corpus, lexical search - not a doc DB fit)\norg-partitioned: the firm's documents never pool across orgs\nsandboxes, per-app git, browser profiles   filesystem\nevent queue (webhook dedup + retry)   SQLite (P-06)\nblobs: screenshots, files, PDFs   filesystem (P-07)\n\nP-08 retired: the Supabase control plane is folded into\nFirestore - credentials, orgs and activation now live\nin the same database (see collections at left).",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
