      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 44172296,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 523654075,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [],
      "boundElements": null,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "rawText": "AS-BUILT 2026-07-11 (integration builder): new persisted collection integration_builder_sessions\n(userId, orgId, integrationKey?, messages[], currentPackage?, validationErrors[]) - the builder\nchat survives restarts. Integration DEFINITIONS gain a runtime tier: <dataDir>/integrations/\nruntime/<key>/ (userCreated: true) shadowing the read-only baseline under api/assets/integrations;\nwritten only by the builder save route after server-side re-validation (reserved baseline keys refused)."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "plat_deltas_branding_20260712",
      "x": 76,
      "y": 768,
      "width": 620,
      "height": 81,
      "text": "Amendment 3 (brand research, 2026-07-12):\njobs.result += colorsApplied + warnings[] (NO_PRIMARY_COLOR fail-loud signal, on jobView too)\nBrandResearchResult += companyName -> org.displayName (never merged into branding)\norg.branding colors: only site-evidence hexes ever merge; neutrals never persist in any slot\norgs += updatedAt (stamped by updateOrg) - the web branding page's re-sync fingerprint",
      "originalText": "Amendment 3 (brand research, 2026-07-12):\njobs.result += colorsApplied + warnings[] (NO_PRIMARY_COLOR fail-loud signal, on jobView too)\nBrandResearchResult += companyName -> org.displayName (never merged into branding)\norg.branding colors: only site-evidence hexes ever merge; neutrals never persist in any slot\norgs += updatedAt (stamped by updateOrg) - the web branding page's re-sync fingerprint",
